3.0 - Revamped to give proper separation between I/F and Model
	- renamed Date object to Mydate
	- better separation between function I/F and model

2.0 - Added functions
	Can now provide offsets to calculate a new date
	or provide any two dates and calculate the number of days between
	eg can now ask:
		+/-{n}		- calculate new date n days from now
		{date}		- (as before) calculate number of days since {date}
		{date} +/-{n}	- calculate new date {n} days from {date}
		{date} {date}	- calculate number of days between dates

	Added testsuite function

1.0 - initial version

Days Since - calculate number of days since a given date
